{% set name = "grunt" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/gruntjs/{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  script: |
    tgz=$(npm pack)
    npm install -g $tgz

requirements:
  build:
    - nodejs

    - npm list -g grunt
  requires:
    - nodejs
